description: This file is the entry point for a React application, importing React, ReactDOM, a CSS stylesheet, and the main App component. It initializes the React root and renders the App component within a StrictMode wrapper.

methods.name: ReactDOM.createRoot
methods.description: Creates a root for rendering a React application into the specified DOM element.

methods.name: root.render
methods.description: Renders React elements into the root DOM node.
